y Of Top-Tier Landscaping Achievements'),(285,86,'hero_subtitle','Explore our gallery to view a selection of our successful commercial landscaping projects. '),(286,86,'hero_button_text','Contact Us'),(287,86,'hero_button_url','/contact-us'),(288,86,'intro_title','Commercial Landscaping Portfolio: See Our Work.'),(289,86,'intro_subtitle','Explore our gallery to view a selection of our successful commercial landscaping projects. From meticulous maintenance to complete landscape design and installation, our portfolio demonstrates our commitment to quality, innovation, and creating exceptional outdoor environments for businesses of all sizes'),(290,86,'_edit_lock','1744739949:1'),(291,86,'_wp_page_template','template-gallery.blade.php'),(322,91,'_wp_attached_file','2025/03/more-sprinklers-min.webp'),(323,91,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1312;s:6:\"height\";i:736;s:4:\"file\";s:32:\"2025/03/more-sprinklers-min.webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:115336;s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:32:\"more-sprinklers-min-150x150.webp\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:8054;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(324,91,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','lots of sprinklers placed around a large lawn'),(327,80,'service_content','<h2 data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:81\">Unlock a Lush, Vibrant Landscape with Expert Irrigation &amp; Water Management</h2>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:328\"><strong>Tired of a lackluster lawn or struggling to keep your landscape thriving?</strong></h3>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:328\">At [Your Company Name - Insert if applicable, otherwise imply], we provide comprehensive irrigation and water management solutions designed to deliver the perfect amount of hydration, ensuring your property in and around the DFW metroplex flourishes.</p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:295\">We offer the best irrigation systems tailored to your unique needs, from efficient residential setups to robust commercial solutions. Our expertise extends to the cutting-edge <strong>Hunter X2™ Controller</strong>, a versatile automatic irrigation system renowned for its reliability and smart features.</p>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:76\"><strong>Experience the Power of Smart Irrigation with the Hunter X2™ Controller:</strong></h3>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:190\">The X2™ Controller, when paired with the optional plug-in <strong>WAND Module</strong> and <strong>Hydrawise™ Software</strong>, puts you in complete control of your landscape\'s hydration, right from your smartphone.</p>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:70\"><strong>Here\'s how the X2™ Controller elevates your irrigation experience:</strong></h3>\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"13:1-21:0\">\n<li data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:280\"><strong>Effortless Remote Management:</strong> Utilize the latest wireless Bluetooth technology with the WAND Module to operate your system remotely via the intuitive Hydrawise App. Perfect for initial setup without Wi-Fi, accessing hard-to-reach controllers, or maintaining a safe distance.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:262\"><strong>Maximize Water Efficiency:</strong> Save time and water with pre-programmed irrigation schedules that can be easily deployed to multiple controllers. Manage an unlimited number of systems and receive instant status updates and alerts through the Hydrawise Software.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:138\"><strong>Unwavering Reliability:</strong> Built with professional contractors in mind, the X2™ Controller offers robust performance and peace of mind.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"16:1-16:194\"><strong>Customizable Control:</strong> Choose from 4, 6, 8, or 14 station fixed models to match your landscape\'s requirements. Enjoy 3 flexible programs with 4 start times each and run times up to 6 hours.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"17:1-17:153\"><strong>Simplified Maintenance:</strong> The QuickCheck™ feature provides easy diagnostics for faulty wiring, while short-circuit protection prevents system damage.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"18:1-18:157\"><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> The backlit display ensures optimal visibility in any lighting conditions. Simplify operation with the \"Hide Programs\" option.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"19:1-19:218\"><strong>Smart Water Management Features:</strong> Prevent water waste and runoff with Cycle and Soak, adjust schedules quickly with Seasonal Adjustment, and easily back up your full irrigation schedule with Easy Retrieve® memory.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"20:1-21:0\"><strong>Protect Your System:</strong> Suspend irrigation for up to 99 days during the off-season and utilize Delay Between Stations for optimal valve and pump performance.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"22:1-22:69\"><strong>With our expert irrigation services, you can:</strong></h3>\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"24:1-28:0\">\n<li data-sourcepos=\"24:1-24:54\"><strong>Achieve a consistently lush and green landscape.</strong></li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"25:1-25:44\"><strong>Optimize water usage and reduce costs.</strong></li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"26:1-26:89\"><strong>Gain confidence knowing your landscape is receiving the precise hydration it needs.</strong></li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"27:1-28:0\"><strong>Enjoy the convenience of smart, automated irrigation.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"29:1-29:367\"><strong>Protect Your Investment</strong></h3>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"29:1-29:367\">We also understand the importance of knowing how to react in case of an emergency. Find helpful guides on how to shut off your sprinkler system in English (<strong>How To Shut Off Your Sprinkler System In Case Of A Leak!</strong>) and Spanish (<strong>Cómo Apagar Su Sistema De Riego En Caso De Una Fuga!</strong>) to prevent further damage in the event of a leak.</p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"31:1-31:196\"><strong>Don\'t leave the health and beauty of your landscape to chance. Contact us today for a consultation and discover the difference a professionally designed and managed irrigation system can make!</strong></p>\n'),(328,80,'feature_type','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"design\";}'),(331,92,'_edit_last','1'),(332,92,'_wp_page_template','/var/www/sandoval-site/web/app/themes/sage/resources/views/template-service.blade.php'),(333,92,'service_description','Get an Instant Green Lawn with Expert Sod Installation!'),(334,92,'service_content','<h2 data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:57\"><strong>Instant Green: Professional Sod Installation Services</strong></h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:298\"><strong>Tired of patchy, bare spots or an uneven lawn? Dream of a lush, vibrant carpet of green without the wait?</strong> Our professional sod installation services provide an immediate transformation for your property, delivering a beautiful, healthy lawn in a fraction of the time it takes to grow from seed.</p>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:32\"><strong>Why Choose Sod Installation?</strong></h3>\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"7:1-13:0\">\n<li data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:141\"><strong>Instant Beauty:</strong> Enjoy a fully established, mature lawn the moment installation is complete. No waiting for seeds to germinate and grow.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:137\"><strong>Erosion Control:</strong> <span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\">Sod provides immediate soil stabilization, preventing erosion and runoff, especially on sloped areas.</span><span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\">   <button class=\"mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger button image-fade-on hide-from-message-actions\" aria-controls=\"sources\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-81\"></button></span>\n<div class=\"container ng-tns-c874500652-197 hide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-container ng-tns-c874500652-197\">\n<div class=\"carousel-content ng-tns-c874500652-197\">\n<div class=\"sources-carousel-source ng-tns-c874500652-197 hide ng-star-inserted\" data-test-id=\"sources-carousel-source\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:121\"><strong><span class=\"citation-1 recitation\">Weed Suppression:</span></strong><span class=\"citation-1 recitation citation-end-1\"> A thick layer of sod acts as a natural barrier, effectively suppressing weed growth.</span><span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\">   <button class=\"mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger button image-fade-on hide-from-message-actions\" aria-controls=\"sources\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-81\"></button></span>\n<div class=\"container ng-tns-c874500652-198 hide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-container ng-tns-c874500652-198\">\n<div class=\"carousel-content ng-tns-c874500652-198\">\n<div class=\"sources-carousel-source ng-tns-c874500652-198 hide ng-star-inserted\" data-test-id=\"sources-carousel-source\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"10:1-10:146\"><strong><span class=\"citation-2 recitation\">Increased Property Value:</span></strong><span class=\"citation-2 recitation citation-end-2\"> A healthy, well-maintained lawn significantly enhances your property\'s curb appeal and overall value.</span><span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\">   <button class=\"mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger button image-fade-on hide-from-message-actions\" aria-controls=\"sources\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-81\"></button></span>\n<div class=\"container ng-tns-c874500652-199 hide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-container ng-tns-c874500652-199\">\n<div class=\"carousel-content ng-tns-c874500652-199\">\n<div class=\"sources-carousel-source ng-tns-c874500652-199 hide ng-star-inserted\" data-test-id=\"sources-carousel-source\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:120\"><strong>Less Maintenance Initially:</strong> Sod requires less intensive care in its initial stages compared to newly seeded lawns.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"12:1-13:0\"><strong>Year-Round Installation (in many climates):</strong> Depending on your location, sod can often be installed outside of traditional seeding seasons.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:40\"><strong>Our Expert Sod Installation Process:</strong></h3>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"16:1-16:104\">Our experienced team ensures a seamless and successful sod installation, following a meticulous process:</p>\n<ol data-sourcepos=\"18:1-23:0\">\n<li data-sourcepos=\"18:1-18:156\"><strong>Site Preparation:</strong> We thoroughly assess your existing soil, grade the area for proper drainage, and remove any debris, rocks, or existing vegetation.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"19:1-19:173\"><strong>Soil Amendment (if necessary):</strong> Based on soil testing, we can amend your soil with nutrients and organic matter to create the ideal foundation for healthy sod growth.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"20:1-20:168\"><strong>Precise Sod Laying:</strong> We carefully lay each roll of premium-quality sod, ensuring tight seams and a level surface for a uniform and aesthetically pleasing result.</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"21:1-21:228\"><strong>Rolling and Initial Watering:</strong> <span class=\"citation-3 recitation citation-end-3\">After laying the sod, we roll the area to ensure good contact between the sod and the soil, promoting root establishment.</span> We also provide thorough initial watering instructions.<span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\">   <button class=\"mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger button image-fade-on hide-from-message-actions\" aria-controls=\"sources\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-81\"></button></span>\n<div class=\"container ng-tns-c874500652-200 hide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-container ng-tns-c874500652-200\">\n<div class=\"carousel-content ng-tns-c874500652-200\">\n<div class=\"sources-carousel-source ng-tns-c874500652-200 hide ng-star-inserted\" data-test-id=\"sources-carousel-source\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"22:1-23:0\"><strong>Clean Up:</strong> We leave your property neat and tidy, with only a beautiful new lawn as evidence of our work.</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"24:1-24:144\"><strong>Invest in an instantly stunning lawn with our professional sod installation services. Contact us today for a free consultation and estimate!</strong></p>\n'),(335,92,'feature_type','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"design\";}'),(336,92,'_edit_lock','1744228271:1'),(337,93,'_wp_attached_file','2025/04/sod-installation-min.webp'),(338,93,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1312;s:6:\"height\";i:736;s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"2025/04/sod-installation-min.webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:166090;s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"sod-installation-min-150x150.webp\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:7160;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(339,93,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','sod being installed'),(344,96,'_edit_last','1'),(345,96,'_edit_lock','1744136122:1'),(346,96,'process_step_number','1'),(347,96,'process_step_short_description','Clear the Area'),(349,96,'process_icon_type','default'),(353,96,'process_title','Our Approach To Sod Installation'),(354,96,'process_subtitle','This is how we do sod installation'),(355,96,'process_associated_services','92'),(356,96,'process_steps','a:1:{i:0;a:4:{s:11:\"step_number\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"step_title\";s:11:\"Lay the sod\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:11:\"Bla bla bla\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}}'),(358,92,'service_process_steps','96'),(360,92,'process_steps','a:8:{i:0;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:31:\"Site Assessment and Measurement\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:267:\"The first step involves evaluating the area to be sodded. This includes measuring the square footage, assessing the existing soil condition, noting any drainage issues, and identifying any obstacles like rocks, roots, or existing vegetation that need to be addressed.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:1;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:28:\"Clearance and Debris Removal\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:240:\"Before any soil preparation can begin, the site needs to be cleared. This involves removing all existing grass, weeds, rocks, roots, and any other debris from the area to ensure a clean surface for the new sod to make contact with the soil.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:2;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:28:\"Soil Preparation and Grading\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:319:\"This crucial step involves preparing the soil to create a healthy foundation for the sod. It may include tilling or loosening compacted soil, amending the soil with topsoil or compost if necessary to improve nutrient content and drainage, and carefully grading the area to ensure proper water runoff and a level surface\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:3;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:30:\"Starter Fertilizer Application\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:262:\"Applying a starter fertilizer specifically formulated for new lawns before laying the sod is highly recommended. This provides essential nutrients directly to the sod roots as they begin to establish in the new soil, promoting healthy growth and quicker rooting.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:4;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:25:\"Sod Delivery and Handling\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:249:\"The fresh sod is typically delivered in rolls. It\'s important to handle these rolls carefully to avoid damage. Ideally, the sod should be installed as soon as possible after delivery, especially in warm weather, to prevent drying out or overheating.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:5;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:22:\"Sod Laying and Fitting\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:309:\"The sod rolls are laid out end-to-end, tightly butted together without overlapping. The installer will typically work in straight lines, similar to laying bricks, staggering the seams between rows to prevent long, continuous lines. Curved areas may require cutting and shaping the sod pieces for a proper fit.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:6;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:28:\"Rolling and Initial Watering\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:342:\"Once the sod is laid, the entire area is typically rolled with a lightweight roller. This ensures good contact between the sod roots and the underlying soil, eliminating air pockets and promoting root establishment. Immediately after rolling, the new sod needs to be thoroughly watered to saturate both the sod and the top few inches of soil.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:7;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:35:\"Post-Installation Care Instructions\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:371:\"The final step involves providing the customer with clear instructions on how to care for their new sod. This typically includes a watering schedule (usually frequent and deep watering in the initial weeks), guidelines on when to mow for the first time, and recommendations for ongoing fertilization and maintenance to ensure a healthy and vibrant lawn for years to come.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}}'),(364,101,'_edit_last','1'),(365,101,'_edit_lock','1744137393:1'),(366,101,'settings','a:8:{s:10:\"menu_title\";s:18:\"Service To Service\";s:2:\"id\";s:18:\"service-to-service\";s:11:\"delete_data\";b:0;s:10:\"reciprocal\";b:0;s:4:\"from\";a:8:{s