al climate.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:5;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:25:\"Professional Installation\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:195:\"Our skilled team expertly installs the flower bed according to the design plan, paying close attention to plant spacing, depth, and arrangement to create a visually appealing and thriving garden.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:6;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:22:\"Mulching and Finishing\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:154:\"We apply a layer of mulch to the flower bed to conserve moisture, suppress weeds, regulate soil temperature, and enhance the overall aesthetic appearance.\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}i:7;a:3:{s:10:\"step_title\";s:32:\"Final Inspection and Walkthrough\";s:16:\"step_description\";s:171:\"We conduct a final inspection to ensure your complete satisfaction and provide detailed care instructions to help you maintain the beauty and health of your new flower bed\";s:9:\"icon_type\";s:7:\"default\";}}'),(513,114,'_wp_attached_file','2025/04/flower-bed-min.webp'),(514,114,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1312;s:6:\"height\";i:736;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2025/04/flower-bed-min.webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:206208;s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"flower-bed-min-150x150.webp\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/webp\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:8794;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(515,114,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','A very colorful flower bed on a lawn'),(579,115,'_form','<label> Your name\n    [text* your-name autocomplete:name] </label>\n\n<label> Your email\n    [email* your-email autocomplete:email] </label>\n\n